The paper describes the implementation of executable scientific papers in the STEM domain, specifically in the Planetary system. This involves the use of semantic annotations and Linked Data to enable interactive services for readers. Based on this description, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries), which deals with the organization, management, and dissemination of digital information. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), as these fields are relevant to the development of interactive and machine-comprehensible scientific papers.
